01:41:15,683 --> 01:41:16,934
<i>Highway's crazy, man.</i>

1181
01:41:41,542 --> 01:41:43,252
<i>They've pulled out, Lieutenant.</i>

1182
01:41:43,795 --> 01:41:45,171
<i>All right, Aponte.</i>

1183
01:41:46,005 --> 01:41:47,340
