1192
01:43:33,571 --> 01:43:38,284
<i>- You run engines as good as your mouth?
- Jones is the name, hot wire is the game.</i>

1193
01:43:38,368 --> 01:43:40,328
<i>Fragetti, go with him.</i>

1194
01:43:48,461 --> 01:43:50,254
- You set? Let's go.
