the Ayatollah of Rock-and-Roll-a.

1198
01:44:39,470 --> 01:44:42,014
<i>You stay right there, sucker.</i>

1199
01:45:23,347 --> 01:45:24,724
Stay low.

1200
01:46:13,022 --> 01:46:14,482
Jesus.

1201
01:46:15,483 --> 01:46:16,943
Please forgive me.

1202
01:46:23,074 --> 01:46:24,534
Let's go.

1203
01:46:44,887 --> 01:46:48,057
<i>Get in there. Tell them who you are,
so no friendlies get hurt.</i>

1204
01:46:48,141 --> 01:46:51,394
<i>Hello, happening hostages.
I'm Stitch Jones, Mr. Funkadelic.</i>

1205
01:46:51,477 --> 01:46:53,104
<i>Try "U.S. Marine," shithead.</i>

1206
01:47:17,295 --> 01:47:18,504
