1207
01:47:34,645 --> 01:47:36,105
United States Marines!

1208
01:47:50,078 --> 01:47:51,454
You've improved.

1209
01:47:52,580 --> 01:47:54,123
Goddamn it. Gunney!

1210
01:48:09,847 --> 01:48:11,808
<i>U.S. Marines, ma'am.</i>

1211
01:48:19,232 --> 01:48:21,693
