- Is everybody all right?

1212
01:48:29,200 --> 01:48:33,037
<i>You know what they say about college,
a behind is a terrible thing to waste.</i>

1213
01:48:33,121 --> 01:48:37,250
Delta Company said they will give us
surfboards and let us go to the beach.

1214
01:48:37,375 --> 01:48:40,712
One student kissed me four times.
I think I'm in love.

1215
01:48:40,878 --> 01:48:43,881
<i>- Was he good-Iooking, Profile?
- It was a girl, Gunney.</i>

1216
01:48:43,965 --> 01:48:46,092
Clean your weapons. Check your ammo.

1217
01:48:48,219 --> 01:48:51,222
<i>All secured, sir.
No casualties, no sign of enemy.</i>

1218
01:48:51,305 --> 01:48:54,726
