1229
01:49:24,255 --> 01:49:25,715
<i>Gunney, recon that hill.</i>

1230
01:49:25,840 --> 01:49:30,386
Wait for Foxtrot Company before
launching any assault. Stay in contact.

1231
01:49:30,970 --> 01:49:34,640
<i>Shall I send back data, sir,
or is that already factored in?</i>

1232
01:49:35,266 --> 01:49:36,726
