1233
01:49:38,227 --> 01:49:42,148
I think Powers is hot for you.
You better watch your back.

1234
01:49:42,231 --> 01:49:44,692
<i>Let's move out, Recon. Form up.</i>

1235
01:50:02,001 --> 01:50:03,169
Keep moving.

1236
01:50:18,226 --> 01:50:19,685
Get down.

1237
01:51:27,462 --> 01:51:29,672
<i>Bad mistake, coming in here like this.</i>

1238
01:51:29,797 --> 01:51:33,551
<i>- It's my fault, Gunney. I led them up here.
- Apologize to their mothers.</i>

1239
01:51:33,676 --> 01:51:34,927
<i>Jesus, Gunney!</i>

1240
01:51:36,512 --> 01:51:38,723
Lay some steel on those targets there.

1241
01:51:39,557 --> 01:51:40,558
Aponte!

1242
01:51:42,560 --> 01:51:44,354
Radio Battalion for air support.

1243
01:51:45,605 --> 01:51:47,482
<i>Gunney, I think Profile is dead.</i>

1244
01:52:01,996 --> 01:52:03,790
<i>Don't let him die, Gunney.</i>

1245
01:52:05,541 --> 01:52:07,168
That's not up to me.

1246
01:52:07,585 --> 01:52:10,338
<i>Come on. Stay down, everyone. Let's go.</i>

1247
01:52:16,344 --> 01:52:17,970
- How you doing?
- I'm okay.

1248
01:52:18,221 --> 01:52:20,181
Doing better than Profile.

1249
01:52:20,473 --> 01:52:22,100
I can still fight.

1250
01:52:22,725 --> 01:52:24,185
We'll make it out of here?

1251
01:52:24,268 --> 01:52:26,562
<i>- You got a date, Collins?
- You never know.</i>

1252
01:52:30,566 --> 01:52:32,193
<i>Gunney, I got Profile killed.</i>

1253
01:52:32,276 --> 01:52:35,947
<i>It was his time.
And when it's your time, your time is up.</i>

1254
01:52:36,072 --> 01:52:37,865
I could have gotten them all killed.

1255
01:52:37,990 --> 01:52:41,077
<i>Yes, but you didn't.
Just don't make the same mistake twice.</i>

1256
01:52:41,369 --> 01:52:42,370
Right.

1257
01:52:42,787 --> 01:52:45,456
I think I figured out a way to call
an air strike...

1258
01:52:45,540 --> 01:52:47,834
...if we can find out where this line is cut.

1259
01:52:47,959 --> 01:52:48,960
Jones!

1260
01:52:49,961 --> 01:52:52,880
<i>- That's my name, loving's my game.
- Thanks for volunteering.</i>

1261
01:52:53,589 --> 01:52:54,590
Say what?

1262
01:52:54,799 --> 01:52:57,635
Get on the roof.
Find out where this line is cut.

1263
01:52:58,052 --> 01:53:00,263
<i>Come on, men. Don't stand there, damn it.</i>

1264
01:53:13,818 --> 01:53:17,155
<i>I wish I was back in New Jersey,
watching The Flintstones.</i>

1265
01:53:17,405 --> 01:53:19,198
This is bullshit.

1266
01:53:23,536 --> 01:53:26,122
Don't you motherfuckers know
who you're shooting at?

1267
01:53:26,247 --> 01:53:28,541
I'm the Ayatollah of Rock-and-Roll-a.

1268
01:53:29,542 --> 01:53:34,005
<i>Big banana-eating, bean-farting
