01:53:36,049 --> 01:53:37,050
Hello?

1271
01:53:38,426 --> 01:53:39,427
It works.

1272
01:53:39,844 --> 01:53:42,930
<i>Damn right, it works.
I almost got my ass shot off for Ma Bell.</i>

1273
01:53:43,890 --> 01:53:45,516
Hello? Operator?

1274
01:53:45,975 --> 01:53:49,812
<i>Yes. I want to make an emergency,
long distance call...</i>

1275
01:53:49,937 --> 01:53:53,608
<i>...to Camp Lejeune, North Carolina.
Collect.</i>

1276
01:53:55,151 --> 01:53:56,152
