1277
01:53:57,904 --> 01:54:00,823
Anybody have a credit card?
They won't make collect calls.

1278
01:54:04,952 --> 01:54:08,623
<i>Have no fear. Stitch is here, and
I never go to combat without my plastic.</i>

1279
01:54:12,794 --> 01:54:13,795
Yes.

1280
01:54:14,379 --> 01:54:16,089
6-6-0...

1281
01:54:16,339 --> 01:54:18,049
...5- 5-8...

1282
01:54:18,633 --> 01:54:20,510
<i>...0- 7- 1-1...</i>

1283
01:54:22,011 --> 01:54:23,638
Camp Lejeune?

1284
01:54:24,555 --> 01:54:26,182
Are you for real?

1285
01:54:27,558 --> 01:54:31,312
Grid 2-1-9...

1286
01:54:31,813 --> 01:54:36,526
...6- 3-2-1-8.

1287
01:54:38,861 --> 01:54:41,531
- Did they get it?
- I don't know. The phone went dead.

1288
01:54:43,282 --> 01:54:44,283
Give me that.

1289
01:54:47,161 --> 01:54:48,705
<i>Gunney, where are you going?</i>

1290
01:54:49,455 --> 01:54:52,125
<i>If they don't see our marker,
we'll be in real trouble.</i>

1291
01:54:52,250 --> 01:54:54,210
But you don't know if we got through.

1292
01:54:54,377 --> 01:54:56,003
<i>We'll have to improvise, sir.</i>

1293
01:55:14,939 --> 01:55:16,232
