1294
01:55:22,780 --> 01:55:24,574
<i>What are we going to do, sir?</i>

1295
01:55:29,746 --> 01:55:31,080
Let's go.

1296
01:56:04,238 --> 01:56:05,782
<i>Don't die, man.</i>

1297
01:56:08,826 --> 01:56:09,827
Gunney!

1298
01:56:12,413 --> 01:56:13,414
Jones.

1299
01:56:15,249 --> 01:56:18,836
Just because we are holding hands
doesn't mean we'll take warm showers...

1300
01:56:18,920 --> 01:56:21,672
